{"tid":1875591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疫情蔓延速度減緩 鐘南山：最快2月中觸頂、4月結束","createTime":"2020-02-12T01:18:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T02:20:54.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"247fe791128a2eccd00051082af61bbd1e2fa7a8","tid":1875591,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T01:18:26.000Z","msg":"中國權威病毒專家、先前對抗SARS一戰成名的鐘南山認為，武漢肺炎有機會在4月受到控制。除此之外，資料顯示疫情的擴散速度似有趨緩，而世界衛生組織(WHO)則將武漢肺炎正式命名為「Covid-19」。<br />\n<br />\n路透社11日獨家報導，先前83歲的鐘南山在接受專訪時指出，從數學模型、近來發生的事件以及政府採取的行動來看，武漢肺炎的蔓延速度有望在本(2)月中旬至月底間觸頂，之後會進入高原期並逐漸減速，或許4月就有望結束。<br />\n<br />\n截至目前為止，中國數據顯示武漢肺炎的復原率相當低，治癒出院病例還不到確診患者的10%。對此，鐘南山表示，當局不願冒任何風險，因此許多病患雖已基本恢復健康、但仍受到隔離。「他們不知道這些患者是否會重新染病，因此治癒出院的比率不是那麼高。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.moneydj.com/KMDJ/News/NewsViewer.aspx?a=3c9e3e47-66c4-404c-967e-258bbef7e0ee\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneydj.com%2FKMDJ%2FNews%2FNewsViewer.aspx%3Fa%3D3c9e3e47-66c4-404c-967e-258bbef7e0ee&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2Bc0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=0cf297a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.moneydj.com/KMDJ/News/NewsViewer.aspx?a=3c9e3e47-66c4-404c-967e-258bbef7e0ee</a>"},{"pid":"b4612dd901379ce872f3c7136775c72bc4398185","tid":1875591,"uid":17313,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T01:20:23.000Z","msg":"呢個人講野好唔可信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64311906c320016f44e601713a2ff586fcb31527","tid":1875591,"uid":276216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T01:20:47.000Z","msg":"又改稿"},{"pid":"477bf0135e3a9b6bade1c9416036438c3b2ba5cc","tid":1875591,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T01:20:55.000Z","msg":"廣東省開工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1ebfa9d01bcfa58eada7dc21b3347f69354c53","tid":1875591,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T01:21:42.000Z","msg":"Ok👌🏻"},{"pid